  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because it was a statement in the archives from the courts, that he had no time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because of the war, we were three months old to make our birth certificate.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it happened after the war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the next time we came, we did not believe that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We gave them time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Please search.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And instead of a birth certificate, I got my mother's death certificate.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In one way, I was happy to find it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But on the other hand, when I saw it black and white, what happened and when, now the chronology of my life was somehow, you know, prearranged now.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Now I knew that this was the time my mother died, that must have been 1942 when I came to my Christian family.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "At least I could figure out what was when.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That helped me.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
